data.text:
Chris Hemsworth (born August 11, 1983) is an Australian actor. He's married to actress and model Elsa Pataky.

He's known for portraying: Kim Hyde in Home and Away and Thor in Thor, The Avengers, Thor: The Dark World, Avengers: Age of Ultron and Thor: Ragnarok.
